---
title: cell_to_coset_evals (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_init_evals : evals = CosetEvals()
    q_init_evals --> q_iter : i = 0
    q_iter --> q_compute : i < FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL
    q_iter --> q_return : i >= FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL
    q_compute --> q_convert : start = i * BYTES_PER_FIELD_ELEMENT
    q_convert --> q_assign : end = (i + 1) * BYTES_PER_FIELD_ELEMENT
    q_assign --> q_iter : evals[i] = bytes_to_bls_field(cell[start:end])
    q_return --> [*] : return evals

    note right of q_iter
        INV: Each cell byte segment [start:end] is exactly BYTES_PER_FIELD_ELEMENT bytes
        INV: Output CosetEvals has exactly FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL elements
    end note
